description:
Walking in obedience to the Lord brings us great peace. In this video, I'm sharing a karaoke version of "Trust and obey" with lyrics. If you're looking for a fun way to worship the Lord, then this is the video for you!
Whether you're a solo karaoke performer or you're gathering a group to join in on the fun, this video is a great way to get into the spirit of worship! Sing along with me as we walk in obedience to the Lord!

Author: John H. Sammis (1887)
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube production!

#ClassicHymn #KarokeLyrics #3Sisters
